      "review_summary": "The PR adds Discord group/channel-only quiet-etiquette prompt guidance and propagates normalized chat type through regular, queued, embedded, snapshot, and compaction agent runs.\n\nPR surface: Source +36, Tests +67. Total +103 across 19 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source inspection gives a high-confidence path: Discord group/channel turns using message-tool-only delivery receive the guidance, while direct-message and automatic-delivery paths do not. The stochastic user-visible outcome has not been reproduced in a real Discord setup.",
